  B   |------<				B   |------<
  C    |------<				C    |------<
  D     |------<			D     |------<
  ---+*------+-------+---		---+--*----+-------+---

  t=2, V=5.5				t=3, V=7.5
  A          |------<			A          |------<
  B           |------<			B           |------<
  C    |------<				C            |------<
  D     |------<			D     |------<
  ---+----*--+-------+---		---+------*+-------+---

Note: 4 identical tasks in FIFO order

~~~

  {A,B}(w=1,r=16) C(w=2,r=16)

  AACCBBCC...
  +---+---+---+---

  t=0, V=1.25				t=2, V=5.25
  A  |--------------<                   A                  |--------------<
